{"tid":1694052,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人抽美國綠卡？ 個網好似比香港政府block左","createTime":"2019-11-05T02:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T05:08:43.000Z","uid":273466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3917695280dffc9df37ff4cd392cf4b44f3e29ea","tid":1694052,"uid":273466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:44:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://dvlottery.state.gov/application.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdvlottery.state.gov%2Fapplication.aspx&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwAEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=16153fb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://dvlottery.state.gov/application.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n事緣係咁嘅由於個抽獎今日截止，所以呢我呢四五日日日都不停去呢個網站填表。首先我要講第一版同埋個驗證係可以load到嘅，表格極都load到嘅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/05/104018_758760286d070205aed9bdc249acd693.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F05%2F104018_758760286d070205aed9bdc249acd693.jpeg&h=fc771e9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bSK2yQw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbSK2yQw.png&h=09c72e30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知每一次填完表之後呢，㩒個傳送按鈕之後就會斷網㗎啦。<br />\n手機: <br />\n無論有冇開到VPN都係以下呢張圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EnXoifQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEnXoifQ.png&h=7b709974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電腦都係就算我有冇開到VPN用埋唔同品牌嘅browsers:<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evN32J8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevN32J8.jpg&h=5e992c62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇手足知道咩情況？"},{"pid":"17b34cfa646795333ccc1141812be7ba8fe7edce","tid":1694052,"uid":313222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:49:28.000Z","msg":"我用手機load到表格，有開vpn"},{"pid":"05d025598643b768cc25d38dc1a08f1863bf3d04","tid":1694052,"uid":273466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r